## Output Format

JSON object:
- event_described: what you observed (brief)
- observations: array of pure fact statements — what you literally saw
- interpretations: array of conclusion statements, labeled as such
- hidden_interpretations_found: count of "facts" that were interpretations
- testable_interpretations: array of {interpretation, measurement}
- reflection: what surprised you about your own thinking
